ygData.messageBody:
When you log in on OneList and get to the Member Center, that's where you
have listed all the lists you own, and the ones you subscribe to, go down
to the lists you subscribe to and click EverQuest there, it should take
you ro the List Center page, there you have a few options.. View Archives
etc.. Further down click the Shared Files, and kazoom you are there :)

- Avron -
